The paper deals with security and privacy concerns related to Android applications, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves software engineering aspects such as developing a monitoring application, which could be categorized under cs.SE. The use of network traffic analysis and categorization of suspicious destinations could be related to information retrieval (cs.IR) or social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper also involves programming language aspects such as developing a lightweight characterization methodology, which could be categorized under programming languages (cs.PL).
